(41, '7', 'forest of swords', 'Consumes HP equal to 10% of Blade\'s Max HP and deals Wind DMG equal to the sum of 20% of his ATK and 50% of his Max HP to a single enemy. In addition, deals Wind DMG equal to the sum of 8% of Blade\'s ATK and 20% of his Max HP to adjacent targets. If Blade\'s current HP is insufficient, his HP will be reduced to 1 when using Forest of Swords. Forest of Swords cannot regenerate Skill Points.', 'Consumes HP equal to 10% of Blade\'s Max HP and deals Wind DMG equal to the sum of 24% of his ATK and 60% of his Max HP to a single enemy. In addition, deals Wind DMG equal to the sum of 9.6% of Blade\'s ATK and 24% of his Max HP to adjacent targets. If Blade\'s current HP is insufficient, his HP will be reduced to 1 when using Forest of Swords. Forest of Swords cannot regenerate Skill Points.', 'Consumes HP equal to 10% of Blade\'s Max HP and deals Wind DMG equal to the sum of 28% of his ATK and 70% of his Max HP to a single enemy. In addition, deals Wind DMG equal to the sum of 11.2% of Blade\'s ATK and 28% of his Max HP to adjacent targets. If Blade\'s current HP is insufficient, his HP will be reduced to 1 when using Forest of Swords. Forest of Swords cannot regenerate Skill Points.', 'Consumes HP equal to 10% of Blade\'s Max HP and deals Wind DMG equal to the sum of 32% of his ATK and 80% of his Max HP to a single enemy. In addition, deals Wind DMG equal to the sum of 12.8% of Blade\'s ATK and 32% of his Max HP to adjacent targets. If Blade\'s current HP is insufficient, his HP will be reduced to 1 when using Forest of Swords. Forest of Swords cannot regenerate Skill Points.', 'Consumes HP equal to 10% of Blade\'s Max HP and deals Wind DMG equal to the sum of 36% of his ATK and 90% of his Max HP to a single enemy. In addition, deals Wind DMG equal to the sum of 14.4% of Blade\'s ATK and 36% of his Max HP to adjacent targets. If Blade\'s current HP is insufficient, his HP will be reduced to 1 when using Forest of Swords. Forest of Swords cannot regenerate Skill Points.', 'Consumes HP equal to 10% of Blade\'s Max HP and deals Wind DMG equal to the sum of 40% of his ATK and 100% of his Max HP to a single enemy. In addition, deals Wind DMG equal to the sum of 16% of Blade\'s ATK and 40% of his Max HP to adjacent targets. If Blade\'s current HP is insufficient, his HP will be reduced to 1 when using Forest of Swords. Forest of Swords cannot regenerate Skill Points.', 'Consumes HP equal to 10% of Blade\'s Max HP and deals Wind DMG equal to the sum of 44% of his ATK and 110% of his Max HP to a single enemy. In addition, deals Wind DMG equal to the sum of 17.6% of Blade\'s ATK and 44% of his Max HP to adjacent targets. If Blade\'s current HP is insufficient, his HP will be reduced to 1 when using Forest of Swords. Forest of Swords cannot regenerate Skill Points.', 2, 30, '60 + 30 adjacent'),
